            "title": "港股開跌412點   科網普跌  百度挫逾7%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數開跌412點或1.52%，報26660，恒生科技指數跌132點或2.22%報5848點 ; 恒生國企指數跌159點或1.67%，報9439點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交34.58億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230712-124434_source-web_09888-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230712-124434_source-web_09888-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：百度官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">百度(09888)跌7.29%，報117元，發布多模態AI智能助手小度，惟無助股價;    阿里巴巴(09988)報156.5元，跌3.4%，成交居首; 京東(09618)跌2.97%，報120.7元，季度調整EBITDA跌逾83%遜預期。騰訊(00700)跌1.68%報，上季度際標準純利升18%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">百濟神州(06160)跌3.49%，報221元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15424244-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e8%b7%8c412%e9%bb%9e-%e7%a7%91%e7%b6%b2%e6%99%ae%e8%b7%8c-%e7%99%be%e5%ba%a6%e6%8c%ab%e9%80%be7",
