        {
            "title": "「the MVP」全數沽清 套現近$25億元 最後一伙5848萬成交 呎價近4萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15415742&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英皇地產港島半山項目「the MVP」今日售出最後一伙單位，全項目117個單位全部售罄，合共套現近25億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">最後售出的一伙單位為26樓A室，實用面積1469平方呎，成交價5848.13萬元，呎價39810元，連車位出售，屬4房(連雙套房)及儲物房大宅，內地買家因心儀半山地段矜罕，故購入單位作自住用途。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「the MVP」當中兩伙特色戶曾以2.66億元成交，成為當時本年度同區分層戶成交價新高；項目最高成交呎價逾4.6萬元水平。同系港島南現樓臨海住宅項目「澄天」尚餘兩伙特色戶待售，將因應目前市況考慮提價發售。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15415742-%e3%80%8cthe-mvp%e3%80%8d%e5%85%a8%e6%95%b8%e6%b2%bd%e6%b8%85-%e5%a5%97%e7%8f%be%e8%bf%9125%e5%84%84%e5%85%83-%e6%9c%80%e5%be%8c%e4%b8%80%e4%bc%995848%e8%90%ac%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e5%91%8e%e5%83%b9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251111_FI_EMPEROR_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-14 09:05:32",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        }
    ]
